{"tid":605032,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［求意見］四月頭東京7日6夜行程","createTime":"2018-03-25T09:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T02:26:20.000Z","uid":2547,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"06dd54c66403f4f9c6e0c2a9791d58b8b54529b5","tid":605032,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"咁大個人第一次去東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早機去 晚機返<br />\n住既係淺草微笑酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行程：<br />\nDay 1: 落左機去埋酒店放行李都4-5點 打算去新宿食下野行下<br />\nDay 2: 上野 ( 上野恩賜錢園睇櫻花 阿美橫町 上町動物園）<br />\nDay 3: 江之島鐮倉一日遊<br />\nDay 4: 台場<br />\nDay 5: 吉祥寺 高圓寺 (井之頭恩賜公園 optional姆明公園）<br />\nDay 6: 橫濱<br />\nDay 7: 淺草 (雷門 二天門 猿江恩賜公園 skytree solamachi ）返歸<br />\n<br />\n好想問下Day 2, 3, 4, 5, 6夜晚可以去邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋咁既行程ok唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e380159f6643f18e0e6897d12fd0ef3b800bbb9","tid":605032,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:50:50.000Z","msg":"大致上無問題啦 不過到時你去到仲有無櫻花都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0e0497d884f2601544668417ab79b4f4899cf8","tid":605032,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e380159f6643f18e0e6897d12fd0ef3b800bbb9","tid":605032,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:50:50.000Z","msg":"大致上無問題啦 不過到時你去到仲有無櫻花都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以睇櫻既行程盡量擺左去頭一兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji